He can perform the '''Essence of Cooperative Attack''' [[Heat Actions|Heat Action]] during his first and second fights. If one of his allies uses said Heat Action near him, he will deliver a jumping push kick to the enemy's face. He emits a red aura in Heat Mode, like every other boss in ''Yakuza 6''. <b>Yuta's moveset is reused by [[Daigo Dojima]] in ''[[Yakuza Kiwami 2]]'' and [[Sakuma]] in ''[[Like a Dragon Gaiden: The Man Who Erased His Name|Like a Dragon Gaiden]]''.</b> == Trivia ==
* Haruka reveals that the first character of Yuta's name was given as the last character of Haruto's name. This is why Haruto is initially only seen with his name spelled with kana, as it would have otherwise given away Yuta as his father. {{EndSpoilers}}

